  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Assess the association of copy number variation (CNV) and inflammatory cytokine with the risk
      of dementia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This is a hospital-based case-control study. We plan to assess the association of CNV and
      inflammatory cytokine with the risk of dementia. Hopefully to find some genetic biomarkers to
      identify the risk of dementia at an early stage.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
